# Canonical source for Ovital Map (奥维互动地图) rules.
# Keep one rule per line using DOMAIN-* / USER-AGENT syntax.
# Derived from capture hosts + public DNS for ovital / geo-compass / siweiearth.

# --- Official brand domains ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ovital.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,www.ovital.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,download.ovital.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,help.ovital.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cloud.ovital.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gps.ovital.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cdn.ovital.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,maps.ovital.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,alt1.ovital.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,alt2.ovital.com

# --- Map tile / imagery services (from capture) ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,geo-compass.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,www.geo-compass.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,omap.geo-compass.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,map.geo-compass.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,api.geo-compass.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tile.geo-compass.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,siweiearth.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,www.siweiearth.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,aoweiservice.siweiearth.com

# --- Related brand / CN sites ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,omap.cn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,www.omap.cn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,aowei.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,www.aowei.com

# --- Catch-all ---
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,ovital
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,aowei
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,geo-compass
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,siweiearth
